• Цвет: черный</p>
<p>Комплектация:<br>
• Зарядное устройство ASOMETECH 72W<br>
• Упаковка</p>',NULL,'retail','WLX-A9T',NULL,'1099.00','false','UAH',NULL,NULL,'100','шт','В наличии',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://images.prom.ua/7537610799_w700_h500_zaryadnoe-ustrojstvo-asometech.jpg','["https://rm5enwhljzam6lbb.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/products/7537610799_w700_h500_zaryadnoe-ustrojstvo-asometech-UVayTXJqqAaHSIo9sTMRatS8onz1Y3.png", "https://rm5enwhljzam6lbb.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/products/7430910810_w700_h500_zaryadnoe-ustrojstvo-asometech-Ge4CLjKKfMIbq8dwejh7JIdItaReiZ.jpg", "https://rm5enwhljzam6lbb.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/products/7430911035_w700_h500_zaryadnoe-ustrojstvo-asometech-ewtHdCDgOPbeDyrI7yM3SM31AeGAXa.jpg", "https://rm5enwhljzam6lbb.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/products/7430911097_w700_h500_zaryadnoe-ustrojstvo-asometech-Y6xuv3lWu9LVIilsyYmB40lr6bZW5C.jpg", "https://rm5enwhljzam6lbb.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/products/7430911329_w700_h500_zaryadnoe-ustrojstvo-asometech-JxSmNPWm4tg8DuofoM0hlVuPn11R6z.jpg", "https://rm5enwhljzam6lbb.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/products/7430911564_w700_h500_zaryadnoe-ustrojstvo-asometech-lkAGH6hk24t8NgRYdfsGnxVmhBgRl5.jpg"]','[]','[]','true','true','false','22','0','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-07-12 15:03:43.500666+00','2026-07-12 15:03:43.500666+00',NULL,'0');
